Package org.whiteflagprotocol.java.core

Class WfMessageCore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.whiteflagprotocol.java.core.WfMessageCore
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    WfMessage
    public class WfMessageCore
extends java.lang.Object
    Whiteflag basic message core class

    This is a class defining a generic basic Whiteflag message. It includes common properties and methods of all message types, and implementation independent logic specified by the Whiteflag standard. All implementation specific logic should be in a derived message subclass.

    Whiteflag standard x-reference:
    4. Message Format
